# Milk Adulteration . Detection

Author: Annika Verma  
B.Tech Food Technology  
Sant Longowal Institute of Engineering and Technology  

## Project Overview
This project focuses on detecting common adulterants in milk such as starch, urea, and detergents using simple laboratory methods.

## File
The complete project report is available in PDF format.

## Importance
Milk adulteration affects quality and safety. This project explains simple detection techniques used in food analysis.
